    Narrative Plan:
    1. Header: Title and period.
    2. KPIs & Conversion: Big numbers and a grouped bar chart for target vs achievement, plus a donut chart for conversion rate.
    3. Success & Challenges: Two-column layout with cards for qualitative insights.
    4. Activity Trend: Bar chart showing successful registrations over time.
    5. Recommendations: A visually structured flowchart-like section.
    Chart Selections:
    - Target vs Achievement: Grouped Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Goal: Compare. Best for direct comparison of two series (Target, Actual) across multiple categories. NO SVG.
    - Conversion Rate: Donut Chart (Chart.js) -> Goal: Inform. Clearly shows a part-to-whole relationship for a key metric. NO SVG.
    - Registrations per Month: Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Goal: Change. Shows performance fluctuations over the reporting period. NO SVG.
    - Recommendations Flow: HTML/CSS Diagram -> Goal: Organize. Structures action items into a clear, sequential process. NO SVG.
